(好似係) <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外兩個字都有人用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣人出晒名成日打錯字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曠古爍今   自己睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20090825000015KK12706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20090825000015KK12706&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=f6be97a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20090825000015KK12706</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原詞應為<span style=\"color: red;\">「震古鑠今」</span>，指：「震動古代，顯耀當世。形容事業或功績非常偉大。」<br />\n<br />\n語例：<br />\n1. 史可法〈復多爾袞書〉：「此等舉動，震古鑠今。」<br />\n2. 譚嗣同《仁學》：「稱震古鑠今之仁政焉。」<br />\n<br />\n「爍」義可通「鑠」，指光亮。故<span style=\"color: red;\">「震古爍今」</span>亦可。<br />\n<br />\n==<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「曠古」，指：「古來所無」、「空前未有」。<br />\n故此「曠古鑠/爍今」義也不通。<br />\n何以古來所罕見之事物，可以顯耀當世？</span><br />\n<br />\n「礫今」，無此語。礫具gravel, pebbles義，無「顯耀」之義，不通於「震古鑠今」之詞義。<br />\n<br />\n故此「曠古礫今」乃錯上加錯，信為習非成是所致。"},{"pid":"7b29ee358b61c28702069eaf208cdc61d941bbaf","tid":222555,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />精辟"},{"pid":"f974e73e11ce694292d81c91af6d0bbb7bc09d04","tid":222555,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘇洵為何作〈六國論〉<br />\n<br />\n《古文評註》：【評】過高候曰：「前幅推原事秦之弊，後幅為六國籌劃一番，歸到正旨作結。<span style=\"color: red;\">蓋宋是時歲輸幣以賂契丹，老泉全是借六國以諷宋</span>，讀者須玩其言在此而意在彼之妙。」<br />\n<br />\